1
00:01:07,660 --> 00:01:08,830
You're finally awake.

2
00:01:08,830 --> 00:01:10,580
You've been unconscious for almost a day.

3
00:01:10,580 --> 00:01:14,310
Your pulse, disturbed by the resentment, has finally stabilized.

4
00:01:17,500 --> 00:01:19,120
Why did you follow me to the border?

5
00:01:19,120 --> 00:01:20,660
You suffered a backlash from that woman's resentment.

6
00:01:20,660 --> 00:01:21,830
Your constitution is still weak.

7
00:01:21,830 --> 00:01:22,700
The border has harsh winds

8
00:01:22,700 --> 00:01:23,160
and heavy resentment.

9
00:01:23,160 --> 00:01:24,660
Without someone to control your pulse

10
00:01:24,660 --> 00:01:25,250
and clear the resentment,

11
00:01:25,250 --> 00:01:26,910
you will sooner or later be unable to stand due to the backlash.

12
00:01:26,910 --> 00:01:27,250
Moreover,

13
00:01:27,250 --> 00:01:29,660
the lantern pattern on my medicine chest is exactly the same as your soul lantern.

14
00:01:29,660 --> 00:01:31,789
I also want to come to the border to investigate the past of Yaowang Valley.

15
00:01:31,789 --> 00:01:33,320
Naturally, I had to follow.

16
00:01:35,160 --> 00:01:37,039
The road ahead is crowded with fleeing refugees.

17
00:01:37,039 --> 00:01:38,840
The carriage can't get through.

18
00:01:43,289 --> 00:01:44,910
There are many souls of those who died unjustly by the roadside,

19
00:01:44,910 --> 00:01:45,830
their resentment lingering.

20
00:01:45,830 --> 00:01:46,700
I will go and cross them over.

21
00:01:46,700 --> 00:01:47,500
Be careful.

22
00:02:08,000 --> 00:02:08,660
A'Deng.

23
00:02:08,660 --> 00:02:10,789
The resentment is backlashing, fast!

24
00:02:10,789 --> 00:02:13,050
Seal the meridians with silver needles.

25
00:02:20,079 --> 00:02:21,160
Take this medicine three times a day

26
00:02:21,160 --> 00:02:22,090
with warm water.

27
00:02:22,160 --> 00:02:23,329
Avoid anything cold.

28
00:02:23,329 --> 00:02:25,329
Children must also be given the exact dosage, understand?

29
00:02:25,329 --> 00:02:28,190
Don't feed them too much, or something will happen.

30
00:02:30,250 --> 00:02:32,329
The medicine for colds and injuries is running out.

31
00:02:32,329 --> 00:02:33,290
If this continues,

32
00:02:33,290 --> 00:02:36,090
the refugees behind us will have no medicine left.

33
00:02:39,250 --> 00:02:40,870
Take two men and ride fast to the county town ahead.

34
00:02:40,870 --> 00:02:43,370
Buy all the common medicines for injuries, colds, and diarrhea.

35
00:02:43,370 --> 00:02:44,829
You must return within half an hour.

36
00:02:44,829 --> 00:02:45,790
Guard this place.

37
00:02:45,790 --> 00:02:46,620
Maintain order.

38
00:02:46,620 --> 00:02:49,620
Don't let the crowded people frighten the two of them.

39
00:02:58,660 --> 00:03:00,200
Only this precious lantern of yours

40
00:03:00,200 --> 00:03:00,910
can both cross over souls

41
00:03:00,910 --> 00:03:01,950
and be used as a candle.

42
00:03:01,950 --> 00:03:03,210
It's quite versatile.

43
00:03:03,410 --> 00:03:04,670
As long as it helps you.

44
00:03:34,910 --> 00:03:37,160
General, you're finally back.

45
00:03:37,329 --> 00:03:38,790
Something strange happened in the camp.

46
00:03:38,790 --> 00:03:41,660
Seven brothers have already committed suicide at night.

47
00:03:41,660 --> 00:03:43,250
Before they died, they all clutched letters from home

48
00:03:43,250 --> 00:03:45,160
and yelled like madmen that they wanted to go home.

49
00:03:45,160 --> 00:03:47,660
The wounds on their bodies were all self-inflicted.

50
00:03:47,660 --> 00:03:48,500
Have you investigated the cause?

51
00:03:48,500 --> 00:03:49,700
Are there any common traits?

52
00:03:49,700 --> 00:03:51,450
I checked. They are all sons of the personal guards

53
00:03:51,450 --> 00:03:53,370
who died in battle with the old general.

54
00:03:53,370 --> 00:03:54,829
They all went to the commanding platform before they died.

55
00:03:54,829 --> 00:03:56,200
The peace amulets given by the old general

56
00:03:56,200 --> 00:03:58,329
that they carried all turned black and cracked.

57
00:03:58,329 --> 00:03:59,450
Word in the camp is that

58
00:03:59,450 --> 00:04:02,450
the old general's ghost has returned to claim lives.

59
00:04:02,660 --> 00:04:04,590
Father died in battle 10 years ago.

60
00:04:04,660 --> 00:04:07,540
The cause of his death was definitely not as simple as the Xiongnu being too powerful.

61
00:04:07,540 --> 00:04:10,000
It was a traitor in the army who cut off our rations

62
00:04:10,000 --> 00:04:11,860
and blocked the reinforcements.

63
00:04:12,830 --> 00:04:14,000
This unsolved case

64
00:04:14,830 --> 00:04:17,560
has always been a thorn in the Xie family's heart.

65
00:04:40,330 --> 00:04:41,159
Xie Lin.

66
00:04:42,159 --> 00:04:44,760
Surrender, and I will keep your corpse intact.

67
00:04:46,830 --> 00:04:49,159
I, Xie Lin, have guarded the territory of Great Yong all my life.

68
00:04:49,159 --> 00:04:51,159
How could I surrender to barbarians like you?

69
00:04:51,159 --> 00:04:52,159
If you want to kill me or torture me,

70
00:04:52,159 --> 00:04:53,370
bring it on.

71
00:05:05,580 --> 00:05:09,580
Thirty years! I have guarded these lands for thirty years,

72
00:05:10,120 --> 00:05:13,000
only to end up like this.

73
00:05:16,370 --> 00:05:17,660
Hand it over to the Master.

74
00:05:17,660 --> 00:05:19,160
Throw the rest of the corpses

75
00:05:19,160 --> 00:05:20,500
into the valley

76
00:05:20,580 --> 00:05:21,620
and let them rot.

77
00:05:21,910 --> 00:05:23,830
Hahaha.

78
00:05:24,040 --> 00:05:24,870
In the resentment,

79
00:05:24,870 --> 00:05:26,160
there is a sinister aura identical to the one on Ying

80
00:05:26,160 --> 00:05:28,330
and Assistant Minister Zhou.

81
00:05:29,040 --> 00:05:32,250
This hostility is definitely not from ordinary dead soldiers.

82
00:05:32,250 --> 00:05:33,620
General Xie Lin's death

83
00:05:33,950 --> 00:05:36,000
must involve a hidden secret.

84
00:05:42,909 --> 00:05:43,830
Lock down the camp.

85
00:05:43,830 --> 00:05:45,450
No soldiers are allowed near the viewing stand.

86
00:05:45,450 --> 00:05:46,780
Arrange a night patrol.

87
00:05:55,000 --> 00:05:56,080
You haven't recovered yet.

88
00:05:56,080 --> 00:05:57,040
Go back and rest.

89
00:05:57,040 --> 00:05:57,580
You don't need to stay with me.
